===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] [[ιστορία]] (''istoria'') "[[history]]".

===Noun===
'''story''' (''plural:'' '''stories''')

# An [[account]] of [[real]] or [[fictional]] [[event]]s.
#:''The [[website]] tells the '''story''' of two [[roommate]]s.''
# A [[lie]].
#:''You’ve been telling '''stories''' again, haven’t you?''

